<template>
Project page

</template>


<script>

export default {
 
  inject:['projects'],

  data() {
    return {
    }
  },
  created(){
    const projectId = this.$route.params.projectId;
    const selectedProject = this.projects.find(project => project.KEY === projectId);
    console.table(selectedProject)
  }

}


</script>


<style></style>
